reviewText: Incredibly gory, goofy and cheap as hell...Return to Yucca Flats: Desert Man Beast has to be seen to believed! More shocking than The Serbian Film and any of The Human Centipede movies. Buy it!

this is trash. the people who made it clearly know it's trash. at the start and ending of the movie they basically give you the middle finger for being stupid enough to watch this piece of trash they made. i repeat, don't waste your time.
